ebkit-box-reflect: unset;\">所以我给大家总结了 4 点</span><span class=\"suffix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span></h3> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(53, 148, 247); font-weight: bold; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat-x: no-repeat; background-repeat-y: no-repeat; background-size: auto; width: auto; height: auto; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: none; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 3px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px;\">结论先行</strong> 直接用一句话总结主题。比如写自律相关的文章。</p> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">就写：今天这篇文章，我想分享最近对自律的一些思考。接着写正文就行。</p> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">无需花哨、技巧和隐晦，直截了当地表明主题。若用户对这话题感兴趣，就会接着看。</p> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">要是不感兴趣，就会关掉。</p> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">反之，若开头绕来绕去，明明写自律，却为吸引用户讲个关联不大的故事，结果就是，用户看到后面觉得被骗，体验更差。</p> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">所以写文章开头，若只选一个方法，那就是——结论先行：用一句话说明文章主题。</p> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(53, 148, 247); font-weight: bold; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat-x: no-repeat; background-repeat-y: no-repeat; background-size: auto; width: auto; height: auto; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: none; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 3px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px;\">举一个生活场景</strong></p> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">在第一点基础上，能进一步优化。</p> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">把文章主题融入一个生活场景，比如写自律——</p> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">前几天，有个朋友找我聊天，说他下班后本打算读书，却忍不住刷抖音了。他觉得自己自律性差，来问我咋办？</p> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">通过大家熟悉的场景，让人有感触，进而觉得：这和我有关！于是就愿意看下去。</p> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice